ith a new episode of alcohol or other drug (AOD) dependence between January 1 and November 15 of the measurement year.',null,null,'Effective Clinical Care','9',null,'58','4','Y','5',null,'1',null,to_date('01-JAN-17','DD-MON-RR'),null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'Y',to_timestamp('01-JAN-18 12.00.00.000000000 AM','DD-MON-RR HH.MI.SSXFF AM'),'1');
